Install our first tool : git

$ yum install git 

Scenario 1: Create a Working directory 

$ mkdir myproject

$ cd myproject

and create 2 files in it

touch index1.html

touch index2.html


Create a local repository


$ git init

It will initialize the repository

how will you know locla repo is created

.git folder will get created

How do you see the .git folder

$ ls -al

$ git status
